cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper is about image processing and computer vision, specifically single image dehazing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel deep learning architecture, which suggests it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the physical rules of hazes, which could place it in the category of cs.GR (Graphics). Finally, the paper extends its proposed model to other vision tasks, such as underwater image enhancement and single image rain removal, which could place it in the category of cs.MM (Multimedia).
